summary: This is an FBI Computer Analysis Response Team (CART) report documenting the creation of a master copy of video images extracted from hard drives seized in New York. The document is marked as sensitive and for official law enforcement use only.

events.title: CART Master Copy Creation
events.description: The FBI's Computer Analysis Response Team created a master copy of video images taken from hard drives seized in New York.

keyFacts: The FBI Computer Analysis Response Team (CART) was involved in analyzing digital evidence.
Video images were extracted from hard drives seized in New York.
A master copy of the video images was created as of June 21, 2021.
The document is marked as sensitive and for official law enforcement use only.
